---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/seo/Breadcrumbs.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Terms of Service', url: '/terms' },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service - Free AI Image Generator No Restrictions"
  description="Terms and conditions for using our free AI image generator no restrictions. Understand your rights when using our uncensored AI image generator without filter."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 md:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbs} />

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-balance mb-6 sm:mb-8">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>

      <div class="space-y-5 sm:space-y-6 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
        <p>Last updated: January 2026</p>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing or using UnrestrictedAI, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must not use our service. Continued use of our free AI image generator no restrictions constitutes acceptance of any updates to these terms.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">2. Eligibility</h2>
          <p>You must be at least 18 years of age to use UnrestrictedAI. By using our service, you represent and warrant that you are at least 18 years old and have the legal capacity to enter into these terms. Our AI image generator no restrictions is intended for adult users only.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">3. Service Description</h2>
          <p>UnrestrictedAI provides an AI-powered image generation service that converts text prompts and categories into images. The service is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without any warranty, express or implied. We strive to maintain high availability but do not guarantee uninterrupted access to our free AI image generator no restrictions.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">4. User Responsibilities</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 sm:pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li>You must not use the service for any illegal activities or purposes prohibited by applicable law</li>
            <li>You must not attempt to abuse, overload, or disrupt our systems or infrastructure</li>
            <li>You are solely responsible for the prompts and categories you select for generation</li>
            <li>You must not use the service to generate content depicting illegal acts or non-consensual material</li>
            <li>You must not attempt to bypass any technical measures or rate limits we may implement</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>You retain all rights to images you generate using our service. We make no claim of ownership over any content generated through our AI image generator no restrictions. By using our service, you grant us a non-exclusive, royalty-free license to process your prompts solely for the purpose of generating images and delivering them to you.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">6. Commercial Use</h2>
          <p>Generated images can be used for commercial purposes, including but not limited to marketing materials, product design, digital art sales, and content creation. However, you may not resell, redistribute, or repackage the generation service itself. You may not use our service to create competing image generation platforms.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">7. Content Guidelines</h2>
          <p>While we are an uncensored AI image generator without filter, you agree not to use our service to create content that:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 sm:pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Depicts illegal activities or violates applicable laws</li>
            <li>Constitutes harassment, hate speech, or incitement to violence</li>
            <li>Infringes upon the intellectual property rights of others</li>
            <li>Depicts non-consensual intimate content or child exploitation (strictly prohibited)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>UnrestrictedAI and its operators shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or exemplary damages arising from the use or inability to use our service, including but not limited to damages for loss of profits, data, or goodwill. Our total liability shall not exceed the amount paid by you to use our service (which is zero, as our service is free).</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">9. Indemnification</h2>
          <p>You agree to indemnify and hold harmless UnrestrictedAI and its operators from any claims, damages, losses, liabilities, and expenses arising from your use of our service, violation of these terms, or infringement of any third-party rights.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">10. Termination</h2>
          <p>We reserve the right to terminate or suspend access to our service at any time, without prior notice, for conduct that we believe violates these terms or is harmful to our service, users, or third parties. Upon termination, your right to use our free AI image generator no restrictions immediately ceases.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">11. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. Continued use of our service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms. We encourage you to review these terms periodically.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">12. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which UnrestrictedAI operates, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2 sm:mb-3">13. Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions about these terms, please visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-brand hover:underline">Contact page</a> or email us at support@unrestrictedai.vercel.app.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
